{"tid":321333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再有四名議員被DQ 立會有足夠票數通過23條","createTime":"2017-07-14T07:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T07:29:36.000Z","uid":121961,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b33da13cb02e6a39bb65f7debcf14421d75145d7","tid":321333,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"講得出呢句嘢嘅人都無乜知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論梁游有無被DQ 另外個四個議員有無被DQ都好<br />\n立法會本身已經有足夠票數通過23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府所提出的議案只需要全體議員的一半票數 就可以獲得通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩三分之二票數係講緊政改方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而直選同功能組別各一半贊成票係講緊由議員所提出的修正案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}